1
00:00:10,960 --> 00:00:13,420
♪The maple mark on your skin♪

2
00:00:14,230 --> 00:00:17,040
♪The only proof we exist♪

3
00:00:18,210 --> 00:00:21,450
♪I stole you back from destiny♪

4
00:00:21,560 --> 00:00:24,430
♪But can I redeem myself♪

5
00:00:24,430 --> 00:00:26,540
♪I don't care what fate foretells♪

6
00:00:26,750 --> 00:00:30,330
♪Or how rough the road may be♪

7
00:00:30,340 --> 00:00:33,280
♪Stay, I'll fight for you♪

8
00:00:33,610 --> 00:00:37,660
♪That's all I'll ever do♪

9
00:00:37,760 --> 00:00:39,890
♪If life is just a show♪

10
00:00:39,890 --> 00:00:42,650
♪I'll stay with you till the end♪

11
00:00:42,650 --> 00:00:44,980
♪I'm scared we'll wake up alone♪

12
00:00:44,980 --> 00:00:47,960
♪So don't let this dream end♪

13
00:00:47,960 --> 00:00:52,420
♪In my bones, in my heart♪

14
00:00:52,420 --> 00:00:54,100
♪I know I'll have to leave♪

15
00:00:54,100 --> 00:00:55,670
♪You must not leave my side♪

16
00:00:55,670 --> 00:00:57,260
♪No place can hold us in♪

17
00:00:57,260 --> 00:01:01,910
♪Not when it's you and me♪

18
00:01:06,890 --> 00:01:10,400
♪Forever♪

19
00:01:11,490 --> 00:01:15,250
♪In my soul♪

20
00:01:17,260 --> 00:01:23,300
=This Palace Maid Isn't Very Calm=
=Episode 11=

21
00:01:35,920 --> 00:01:38,200
The ball game for favor, finally.

22
00:01:38,840 --> 00:01:39,710
Sorry,

23
00:01:39,710 --> 00:01:40,640
Xiao Rou.

24
00:01:40,640 --> 00:01:43,350
- You won't win today.
- Come on.

25
00:01:46,280 --> 00:01:47,120
Come on.

26
00:01:50,230 --> 00:01:51,070
Miss Xiao.

27
00:01:58,230 --> 00:01:59,070
Wait.

28
00:02:03,230 --> 00:02:04,640
Greetings, Lady Xiao.

29
00:02:04,790 --> 00:02:06,040
Then join us.

30
00:02:07,150 --> 00:02:08,190
Thank you.

31
00:02:15,190 --> 00:02:16,030
Here.

32
00:02:24,080 --> 00:02:25,680
Why's the garden so lively?

33
00:02:25,680 --> 00:02:26,520
Pass it to me.

34
00:02:26,710 --> 00:02:29,560
Your Majesty, the new ladies

35
00:02:29,560 --> 00:02:31,150
must be playing.

36
00:02:31,910 --> 00:02:32,750
Slow down.

37
00:02:36,150 --> 00:02:37,470
Hurry, Miss Xiao.

38
00:02:37,470 --> 00:02:38,840
Over here.

39
00:02:41,030 --> 00:02:42,240
Pass it.

40
00:02:44,840 --> 00:02:45,680
Go.

41
00:02:55,360 --> 00:02:56,200
Watch out!

42
00:03:07,400 --> 00:03:08,360
Lady Xiao.

43
00:03:08,680 --> 00:03:09,520
It's…

44
00:03:10,160 --> 00:03:11,000
I have duties.

45
00:03:11,000 --> 00:03:12,150
I'll return to Cining Palace.

46
00:03:12,310 --> 00:03:13,150
You…

47
00:03:14,680 --> 00:03:16,080
What do we do?

48
00:03:17,470 --> 00:03:18,750
I don't know.

49
00:03:21,840 --> 00:03:23,680
Greetings, Your Majesty.

50
00:03:24,630 --> 00:03:27,400
Weren't you at the consort selection?

51
00:03:27,770 --> 00:03:28,630
Your Majesty,

52
00:03:28,630 --> 00:03:29,710
this is Attendant Hui.

53
00:03:29,710 --> 00:03:31,030
The one

54
00:03:31,030 --> 00:03:32,960
who attracted a bee.

55
00:03:34,150 --> 00:03:35,150
Are you hurt?

56
00:03:37,560 --> 00:03:38,750
What's in your basket?

57
00:03:39,430 --> 00:03:41,000
Thank you, Your Majesty.

58
00:03:41,000 --> 00:03:42,030
I'm fine.

59
00:03:42,190 --> 00:03:44,360
Just some peonies for cooking.

60
00:03:44,360 --> 00:03:47,400
Good for health and fragrance.

61
00:03:47,800 --> 00:03:49,030
You're young,

62
00:03:49,120 --> 00:03:50,560
yet knowledgeable.

63
00:03:50,840 --> 00:03:52,870
I overheard herbal studies

64
00:03:52,870 --> 00:03:54,310
by my father's study.

65
00:03:54,310 --> 00:03:56,120
That's how I know

66
00:03:56,150 --> 00:03:57,190
a few medicinal plants.

67
00:03:57,710 --> 00:03:58,550
Remarkable.

68
00:03:58,870 --> 00:03:59,960
Impressive knowledge

69
00:03:59,960 --> 00:04:01,630
for a lady.

70
00:04:01,630 --> 00:04:03,630
What do you read?

71
00:04:04,190 --> 00:04:05,360
I like

72
00:04:06,080 --> 00:04:07,150
poetry.

73
00:04:08,310 --> 00:04:09,430
What kind?

74
00:04:09,560 --> 00:04:11,520
Much poetry I enjoy,

75
00:04:12,000 --> 00:04:14,150
but in this moment, in this setting,

76
00:04:14,400 --> 00:04:16,070
one short poem

77
00:04:16,070 --> 00:04:17,720
comes to mind.

78
00:04:18,920 --> 00:04:21,360
Wine and verse, flowers urge a toast.

79
00:04:21,630 --> 00:04:24,270
Refining lines I love the most.

80
00:04:24,920 --> 00:04:27,480
In palace halls, no friend is near.

81
00:04:28,240 --> 00:04:31,800
Moon and breeze, my soul-mates dear.

82
00:04:32,040 --> 00:04:32,920
Isn't that

83
00:04:33,120 --> 00:04:36,000
Your Majesty's poem?

84
00:04:38,600 --> 00:04:39,830
How do you know it?

85
00:04:39,950 --> 00:04:42,830
From an old book chamber.

86
00:04:42,920 --> 00:04:44,000
So I committed it to memory.

87
00:04:46,160 --> 00:04:47,120
It seems

88
00:04:47,600 --> 00:04:48,920
we're meant

89
00:04:49,120 --> 00:04:50,510
to meet after all.

90
00:04:59,000 --> 00:05:00,750
Main plot triggered.

91
00:05:00,830 --> 00:05:02,000
They clicked

92
00:05:02,000 --> 00:05:03,430
three years early.

93
00:05:03,430 --> 00:05:04,270
Yes!

94
00:05:05,000 --> 00:05:07,630
The jerk Emperor

95
00:05:07,630 --> 00:05:08,630
always targets me.

96
00:05:08,950 --> 00:05:10,950
Yet here I am, fixing his love life.

97
00:05:10,950 --> 00:05:12,070
I'm too kind.

98
00:05:12,680 --> 00:05:13,720
Time to go home.

99
00:05:21,560 --> 00:05:22,480
What a show.

100
00:05:24,160 --> 00:05:25,830
Greetings, Your Highness.

101
00:05:25,830 --> 00:05:27,270
Today's setup

102
00:05:28,040 --> 00:05:29,510
is textbook-level.

103
00:05:30,120 --> 00:05:31,000
Except

104
00:05:31,190 --> 00:05:32,680
it was too precise.

105
00:05:33,390 --> 00:05:35,830
One would need to see the future

106
00:05:36,310 --> 00:05:37,920
to pull it off.

107
00:05:38,870 --> 00:05:41,950
I don't know what you mean.

108
00:05:43,190 --> 00:05:44,030
Really?

109
00:05:44,560 --> 00:05:45,480
Then,

110
00:05:45,720 --> 00:05:47,040
let me tell you a story.

111
00:05:47,480 --> 00:05:48,360
In this dynasty,

112
00:05:48,510 --> 00:05:50,310
there was once an Imperial Preceptor.

113
00:05:50,720 --> 00:05:51,720
He claimed

114
00:05:51,720 --> 00:05:53,920
he had been favored by an immortal

115
00:05:54,390 --> 00:05:56,390
and could foresee the future.

116
00:05:56,600 --> 00:05:57,480
After that,

117
00:05:57,480 --> 00:05:59,600
he foretold many things for Father.

118
00:06:00,120 --> 00:06:03,190
Many of his prophecies

119
00:06:03,800 --> 00:06:05,720
came true in the end.

120
00:06:06,000 --> 00:06:07,040
I believe

121
00:06:08,190 --> 00:06:10,190
you're just like him.

122
00:06:10,800 --> 00:06:11,830
Me?

123
00:06:12,040 --> 00:06:13,870
How could that be?

124
00:06:13,870 --> 00:06:15,510
Foretell the future?

125
00:06:15,510 --> 00:06:17,270
What you saw was all

126
00:06:17,630 --> 00:06:18,480
a coincidence.

127
00:06:19,160 --> 00:06:20,000
Is that so?

128
00:06:20,000 --> 00:06:20,840
Mm.

129
00:06:21,190 --> 00:06:22,390
You know His Majesty's schedule

130
00:06:22,600 --> 00:06:23,800
down to the exact detail.

131
00:06:24,360 --> 00:06:25,430
You also know exactly

132
00:06:25,430 --> 00:06:27,160
when and where the candidates

133
00:06:27,160 --> 00:06:28,600
would pass the ball in the garden.

134
00:06:28,750 --> 00:06:30,560
Even where the ball would land,

135
00:06:30,750 --> 00:06:32,390
you guessed it perfectly.

136
00:06:32,870 --> 00:06:34,270
And yet you tell me

137
00:06:34,270 --> 00:06:35,950
it's all a coincidence?

138
00:06:35,950 --> 00:06:36,790
I...

139
00:06:37,120 --> 00:06:39,190
I was just lucky.

140
00:06:41,120 --> 00:06:42,920
When we first met,

141
00:06:43,240 --> 00:06:46,070
you predicted the Dowager's illness.

142
00:06:46,600 --> 00:06:48,360
At the time, I thought nothing of it.

143
00:06:48,720 --> 00:06:50,310
Just a coincidence.

144
00:06:50,560 --> 00:06:52,720
But everything that happened afterward

145
00:06:53,160 --> 00:06:55,750
made I realize you have a secret.

146
00:06:56,630 --> 00:06:57,630
Secret?

147
00:07:00,750 --> 00:07:02,270
I don't have one.

148
00:07:02,680 --> 00:07:04,720
Are you kidding? No secret.

149
00:07:04,720 --> 00:07:05,750
Follow me.

150
00:07:07,560 --> 00:07:08,400
I…

151
00:07:09,160 --> 00:07:11,390
Seriously?

152
00:07:18,920 --> 00:07:19,760
Here.

153
00:07:20,120 --> 00:07:23,120
These are the files from my spies.

154
00:07:23,360 --> 00:07:24,200
Look for yourself.

155
00:07:28,800 --> 00:07:29,920
On June 7,

156
00:07:30,000 --> 00:07:31,830
Ye Jin exposed Yunxi

157
00:07:31,830 --> 00:07:33,480
for poisoning Zhi Hui,

158
00:07:33,560 --> 00:07:36,000
which sent Yunxi to the Cold Palace.

159
00:07:36,270 --> 00:07:37,160
On June 8,

160
00:07:37,160 --> 00:07:39,390
Ye Jin advised Consort Lan
to host a banquet.

161
00:07:39,600 --> 00:07:40,830
On June 9,

162
00:07:40,830 --> 00:07:43,560
Liu Mei defied Consort Lan at the banquet

163
00:07:43,560 --> 00:07:44,830
and was punished for it.

164
00:07:45,190 --> 00:07:46,390
On June 10,

165
00:07:46,480 --> 00:07:49,680
Xiao Rou was disfigured by a rouge allergy.

166
00:07:49,680 --> 00:07:50,600
During that time,

167
00:07:51,390 --> 00:07:53,270
Ye Jin entered her chamber.

168
00:07:54,270 --> 00:07:55,600
You're spying on me?

169
00:07:55,920 --> 00:07:56,760
Yes.

170
00:07:56,950 --> 00:07:58,630
Because I couldn't read you.

171
00:07:59,040 --> 00:08:00,190
I wanted to know

172
00:08:00,190 --> 00:08:01,480
who you really are.

173
00:08:03,880 --> 00:08:04,750
I...

174
00:08:04,870 --> 00:08:06,800
My records are at the Ministry.

175
00:08:06,870 --> 00:08:09,390
My age, origin, family,
and year I entered the palace

176
00:08:09,390 --> 00:08:10,920
can all be verified.

177
00:08:12,040 --> 00:08:13,480
A case file can be forged.

178
00:08:13,750 --> 00:08:15,120
But a person's bearing

179
00:08:15,310 --> 00:08:16,190
cannot be faked.

180
00:08:16,560 --> 00:08:18,600
From the moment I saw you,

181
00:08:18,750 --> 00:08:19,950
I knew

182
00:08:20,240 --> 00:08:21,390
you were different.

183
00:08:21,870 --> 00:08:23,720
And these files

184
00:08:23,920 --> 00:08:25,390
prove it.

185
00:08:25,830 --> 00:08:28,560
Your moves against them seem normal.

186
00:08:28,560 --> 00:08:29,720
But every step

187
00:08:29,920 --> 00:08:32,030
is calculated.

188
00:08:33,030 --> 00:08:34,510
As if you knew what was coming.

189
00:08:35,480 --> 00:08:36,360
Like

190
00:08:36,750 --> 00:08:37,750
today's

191
00:08:38,000 --> 00:08:39,910
ball game.

192
00:08:43,080 --> 00:08:44,360
What do you want?

193
00:08:46,790 --> 00:08:47,720
Although

194
00:08:47,720 --> 00:08:49,600
I know your secret,

195
00:08:50,080 --> 00:08:51,000
for now,

196
00:08:51,200 --> 00:08:52,390
I don't intend to use it.

197
00:08:52,790 --> 00:08:54,200
As long as you behave,

198
00:08:54,960 --> 00:08:55,840
I will

199
00:08:56,870 --> 00:08:58,670
keep your secret safe.

200
00:08:59,840 --> 00:09:02,030
If you wanted to keep it safe,

201
00:09:02,030 --> 00:09:04,510
you wouldn't show me this.

202
00:09:04,840 --> 00:09:06,910
There's a catch, isn't there?

203
00:09:07,270 --> 00:09:08,320
Smart indeed.

204
00:09:10,480 --> 00:09:11,550
In return,

205
00:09:11,960 --> 00:09:13,150
you'll help me

206
00:09:13,150 --> 00:09:14,670
with a small problem.

207
00:09:15,200 --> 00:09:16,240
What problem?

208
00:09:17,200 --> 00:09:18,790
After having a conversation

209
00:09:18,790 --> 00:09:20,270
with Tongjia Baozhu,

210
00:09:21,000 --> 00:09:23,200
Mother insists I marry her.

211
00:09:23,600 --> 00:09:25,150
She's inviting her to the palace soon.

212
00:09:25,510 --> 00:09:27,200
I'm done playing along.

213
00:09:27,480 --> 00:09:28,600
You need to find

214
00:09:29,150 --> 00:09:30,320
a way out for me.

215
00:09:34,390 --> 00:09:37,480
By Imperial Decree,

216
00:09:37,480 --> 00:09:39,790
First Attendant of the Niohuru clan

217
00:09:39,790 --> 00:09:41,480
is gentle and gracious,

218
00:09:41,480 --> 00:09:43,200
elegant in bearing and pleasing in manner,

219
00:09:43,200 --> 00:09:45,000
virtuous and prudent by nature.

220
00:09:45,000 --> 00:09:46,600
A model of gentleness and grace.

221
00:09:46,600 --> 00:09:48,390
You have deeply pleased His Majesty.

222
00:09:48,390 --> 00:09:50,790
You are hereby promoted to Noble Lady.

223
00:09:50,790 --> 00:09:52,550
Respect this decree.

224
00:10:00,480 --> 00:10:01,320
Your Ladyship.

225
00:10:01,440 --> 00:10:02,360
Look.

226
00:10:02,600 --> 00:10:04,200
This silk robe

227
00:10:04,200 --> 00:10:06,390
is the finest tribute.

228
00:10:06,600 --> 00:10:08,790
The color suits your skin perfectly.

229
00:10:09,150 --> 00:10:11,360
And this jade bracelet.

230
00:10:11,400 --> 00:10:12,550
It's so clear and beautiful.

231
00:10:12,550 --> 00:10:14,200
It will look lovely on you.

232
00:10:14,600 --> 00:10:15,440
And this as well.

233
00:10:15,840 --> 00:10:18,390
The bird's nest soup.

234
00:10:18,600 --> 00:10:20,360
They said His Majesty ordered it

235
00:10:20,360 --> 00:10:21,550
to help restore your strength.

236
00:10:21,840 --> 00:10:23,550
His Majesty truly favors you.

237
00:10:24,390 --> 00:10:25,270
Just leave it there.

238
00:10:26,600 --> 00:10:27,630
Your Ladyship.

239
00:10:27,630 --> 00:10:29,030
Why the long face?

240
00:10:29,390 --> 00:10:32,030
You were promoted overnight.

241
00:10:32,270 --> 00:10:34,270
His Majesty sent three rounds of gifts.

242
00:10:34,720 --> 00:10:36,080
You should be happy.

243
00:10:37,000 --> 00:10:38,150
I'm not unhappy.

244
00:10:39,000 --> 00:10:40,000
It is just that...

245
00:10:42,510 --> 00:10:43,600
I feel a little weary.

246
00:10:45,550 --> 00:10:46,440
Noble Lady Hui.

247
00:10:46,790 --> 00:10:49,360
Consort Lan sent these hairpins

248
00:10:49,390 --> 00:10:50,840
to congratulate you.

249
00:10:54,390 --> 00:10:55,320
Consort Duan

250
00:10:55,320 --> 00:10:57,320
sent this jade amulet.

251
00:10:57,720 --> 00:10:59,600
She wishes you good health

252
00:10:59,600 --> 00:11:00,510
and a bright future.

253
00:11:02,080 --> 00:11:03,840
My thanks.

254
00:11:04,240 --> 00:11:06,510
But my rank is too low

255
00:11:06,510 --> 00:11:08,200
for such honor.

256
00:11:08,910 --> 00:11:11,080
Tell them I appreciate the gesture,

257
00:11:11,240 --> 00:11:14,550
but I cannot accept these gifts.

258
00:11:15,030 --> 00:11:17,150
Please forgive me.

259
00:11:17,720 --> 00:11:18,750
- Yes.
- Yes.

260
00:11:23,030 --> 00:11:23,960
Your Ladyship.

261
00:11:24,440 --> 00:11:26,360
Why refuse?

262
00:11:26,790 --> 00:11:28,000
You might offend them.

263
00:11:29,080 --> 00:11:32,000
They are always at each other's throats.

264
00:11:32,550 --> 00:11:34,630
It's no coincidence

265
00:11:34,960 --> 00:11:36,270
they both sent gifts.

266
00:11:36,790 --> 00:11:38,030
If I take one,

267
00:11:38,030 --> 00:11:39,510
I offend the other.

268
00:11:39,840 --> 00:11:41,270
If I take both,

269
00:11:41,740 --> 00:11:42,600
I will

270
00:11:42,600 --> 00:11:43,750
be in their debt.

271
00:11:46,240 --> 00:11:47,270
Better to just

272
00:11:47,600 --> 00:11:48,720
stay out of it.

273
00:11:58,150 --> 00:11:59,910
That Noble Lady Hui.

274
00:12:01,150 --> 00:12:02,870
I try to be kind,

275
00:12:03,600 --> 00:12:04,840
and she brushes me off.

276
00:12:05,790 --> 00:12:07,510
How ungrateful.

277
00:12:08,030 --> 00:12:09,080
Your Highness.

278
00:12:09,080 --> 00:12:11,080
She rejected Consort Lan's gift too.

279
00:12:11,510 --> 00:12:12,960
She's being cautious.

280
00:12:13,390 --> 00:12:14,440
At least

281
00:12:14,440 --> 00:12:16,000
she hasn't picked a side yet.

282
00:12:16,910 --> 00:12:17,870
But now,

283
00:12:18,080 --> 00:12:19,750
these candidates

284
00:12:20,150 --> 00:12:22,360
are all flocking to Consort Lan.

285
00:12:23,000 --> 00:12:25,600
None of them respect me.

286
00:12:27,360 --> 00:12:29,270
At long last, there is a Noble Lady Hui,

287
00:12:30,150 --> 00:12:31,030
and yet

288
00:12:32,150 --> 00:12:33,600
she acts superior.

289
00:12:35,360 --> 00:12:36,480
Now,

290
00:12:37,080 --> 00:12:38,360
I'm heavily pregnant

291
00:12:39,080 --> 00:12:40,510
and can't attend the Emperor.

292
00:12:41,510 --> 00:12:42,480
I can't

293
00:12:44,000 --> 00:12:45,320
just let Consort Lan

294
00:12:45,320 --> 00:12:47,870
take over the palace.

295
00:12:48,550 --> 00:12:49,750
Don't bother

296
00:12:50,240 --> 00:12:53,360
with strangers.

297
00:12:53,750 --> 00:12:54,960
Promote one of our own.

298
00:12:55,600 --> 00:12:56,600
Our own?

299
00:12:57,790 --> 00:12:58,630
Who?

300
00:12:58,910 --> 00:13:00,200
Do you remember

301
00:13:00,440 --> 00:13:02,240
a candidate named Liu Mei?

302
00:13:03,390 --> 00:13:05,200
She missed the selection due to illness.

303
00:13:05,670 --> 00:13:07,240
She has no rank or favor

304
00:13:08,030 --> 00:13:09,960
and is desperate.

305
00:13:10,200 --> 00:13:11,360
If you help her

306
00:13:11,360 --> 00:13:12,910
at a time like this,

307
00:13:13,240 --> 00:13:15,320
she'll be loyal to you forever.

308
00:13:17,670 --> 00:13:18,720
Liu Mei?

309
00:13:20,550 --> 00:13:21,960
I remember her.

310
00:13:23,030 --> 00:13:24,200
She's pretty,

311
00:13:25,390 --> 00:13:26,790
but not very bright.

312
00:13:26,790 --> 00:13:28,360
Even better.

313
00:13:28,600 --> 00:13:29,720
Her father

314
00:13:29,720 --> 00:13:32,270
served your family for years.

315
00:13:32,840 --> 00:13:35,120
He's still in the army.

316
00:13:36,080 --> 00:13:37,600
Her family

317
00:13:37,840 --> 00:13:39,510
depends on us.

318
00:13:40,000 --> 00:13:41,080
People like her

319
00:13:41,390 --> 00:13:42,360
are easy to manage

320
00:13:43,030 --> 00:13:44,000
and easy to use.

321
00:13:44,390 --> 00:13:46,000
She would be useful to you.

322
00:13:47,600 --> 00:13:48,750
You're right.

323
00:13:49,600 --> 00:13:50,440
Tomorrow,

324
00:13:51,150 --> 00:13:52,600
have her come see me.

325
00:13:53,030 --> 00:13:53,870
Yes.

326
00:13:56,320 --> 00:13:57,320
Your Highness,

327
00:13:57,670 --> 00:13:59,320
that Noble Lady Hui is favored,

328
00:13:59,510 --> 00:14:00,750
not for her looks,

329
00:14:01,000 --> 00:14:02,270
but for her talent.

330
00:14:02,840 --> 00:14:04,390
When she is with His Majesty,

331
00:14:04,390 --> 00:14:06,440
they read poems together.

332
00:14:08,150 --> 00:14:10,120
What does she read?

333
00:14:10,360 --> 00:14:11,840
What poems?

334
00:14:12,080 --> 00:14:13,600
I don't know the poems.

335
00:14:13,910 --> 00:14:14,910
But currently,

336
00:14:15,750 --> 00:14:17,000
she's reading "Book of Han."

337
00:14:17,390 --> 00:14:19,120
Noble Lady Hui told the story

338
00:14:19,550 --> 00:14:21,910
of Emperor Wu of Han
and Empress Dowager Dou.

339
00:14:22,150 --> 00:14:23,270
His Majesty was fascinated.

340
00:14:23,870 --> 00:14:24,910
He praised her

341
00:14:25,360 --> 00:14:26,840
for being learned

342
00:14:26,840 --> 00:14:28,030
and called her his soulmate.

343
00:14:28,320 --> 00:14:30,870
Emperor Wu and Dowager Dou?

344
00:14:33,870 --> 00:14:35,000
Interesting.

345
00:14:36,200 --> 00:14:39,720
Their bond is already strained

346
00:14:39,960 --> 00:14:42,720
yet she dares discuss it.

347
00:14:45,360 --> 00:14:47,550
She's got nerve.

348
00:14:48,600 --> 00:14:51,600
How would the Dowager feel

349
00:14:52,320 --> 00:14:54,320
if she heard that?

350
00:14:54,960 --> 00:14:58,480
Go spread that story.

351
00:14:58,480 --> 00:15:00,120
Exaggerate her words.

352
00:15:00,750 --> 00:15:02,910
If the Dowager gets angry,

353
00:15:03,390 --> 00:15:05,670
you'll be rewarded.

354
00:15:06,000 --> 00:15:06,960
Understood.

355
00:15:07,120 --> 00:15:08,270
I'll get on it.

356
00:15:11,390 --> 00:15:12,910
Talent?

357
00:15:13,960 --> 00:15:17,030
The palace is full of it.

358
00:15:17,360 --> 00:15:18,480
What's rare

359
00:15:19,200 --> 00:15:22,270
is knowing one's place.

360
00:15:26,960 --> 00:15:29,400
♪I am but an outsider♪

361
00:15:29,440 --> 00:15:31,600
♪Yet something drags me deeper♪

362
00:15:31,840 --> 00:15:35,880
♪Outwit the world but not the way we meet♪

363
00:15:35,880 --> 00:15:40,120
♪Splendid blooms line deadly ground♪

364
00:15:44,400 --> 00:15:47,640
♪Life's a phantom, yet I find you♪

365
00:15:47,800 --> 00:15:51,200
♪In a world of lies, you're all that's clear♪

366
00:15:51,200 --> 00:15:53,720
♪I know how this story ends♪

367
00:15:53,720 --> 00:15:58,280
♪I still want what's in your eyes♪

368
00:15:58,600 --> 00:16:02,720
♪Truth or lieI can't tell♪

369
00:16:07,680 --> 00:16:11,000
♪You hide it all behind your lines♪

370
00:16:11,000 --> 00:16:14,280
♪So familiar, yet out of reach♪

371
00:16:14,480 --> 00:16:17,560
♪A history that no one can search♪

372
00:16:17,800 --> 00:16:21,080
♪Like you drift in from another star♪

373
00:16:21,120 --> 00:16:22,880
♪I am but an outsider♪

374
00:16:22,880 --> 00:16:25,120
♪Yet something drags me deeper♪

375
00:16:25,120 --> 00:16:29,160
♪Outwit the world but not the way we meet♪

376
00:16:29,160 --> 00:16:33,840
♪Splendid blooms line deadly ground♪

377
00:16:37,760 --> 00:16:41,160
♪Life's a phantom, yet I find you♪

378
00:16:41,160 --> 00:16:44,520
♪In a world of lies, you're all that's clear♪

379
00:16:44,520 --> 00:16:47,000
♪I know how this story ends♪

380
00:16:47,000 --> 00:16:51,160
♪I still want what's in your eyes♪

381
00:16:51,160 --> 00:16:54,440
♪When it's over and I'm gone♪

382
00:16:54,440 --> 00:16:58,240
♪Please forget me and move on♪

383
00:16:58,240 --> 00:17:04,480
♪Just let this absurd dream fade♪

384
00:17:07,640 --> 00:17:16,000
♪Snow hides our tracks♪

385
00:17:19,560 --> 00:17:29,280
♪When do I finally wake♪
